============================================================
WAVE 2 — FIX / CLOSE (parallel; spawn after Wave 1 returns)
============================================================
{{WAVE_2_CONSUMER_BLOCKS}}

Consumer rules:
- First action: `ls .orchestrator/tasks/inbox/` and filter by consumer_role.
- Pickup: move inbox/ → in-progress/ + stamp `## Activity`.
- Close: append `## Resolution` then move to done/.
- Escalate (if too big/unclear): append `## Escalation reason` then move to
  escalated/. NEVER delete.

============================================================
WAVE 3 — RE-VERIFY (spawn after Wave 2 returns)
============================================================
RV (subagent_type=tester, isolation=worktree):
- Consume consumer_role=re-verifier tickets from inbox/.
- Run the full project gate suite against each Wave-2 fixer branch
  (per-branch — do NOT integrate). For each branch, file any NEW red as a
  .todo.md with consumer_role=re-verifier and priority=high.

